    dc:description "Fig. 25. Kornia fibula sp. nov. A. Paratype MB.C.31069.2 (Weyer 1993–1994 Coll.) from Oberrödinghausen, bed 2a. B. Holotype MB.C.5260.3 (Weyer 1993–1994 Coll.) from Oese, bed 28. Scale bar units =1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8177631/files/figure.png" ;
