<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8177633>
    dc:description "Fig. 26. Kornia fibula sp. nov. A. Cross section of paratype MB.C.31069.1 (Weyer 1993–1994 Coll.) from Oberrödinghausen, bed 2a. B. Growth line course of holotype MB.C.5260.3 (Weyer 1993–1994 Coll.) from Oese, bed 28, at dm=9.8 mm, ww =9.9 mm, wh= 4.8 mm. C–E. Ontogenetic development of the conch width index (ww/dm), umbilical width index (uw/dm), whorl width index (ww/wh) and whorl expansion rate (WER) of selected specimens. Scale bar units=1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8177633/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

